Responses in JRG: 
The documentation for SAPI is available in HTML, but it is a part of the Software Development Kit (SDK)[1] as a local resource. 
There does not appear to be a similar resource for SAPI on the Web. 
The requirement should be to allow the user to user to set parameters anywhere with in the range of the synthesizer and that the user agent should provide information on the ranges available. 
